Package controller

Interface Registry<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the key used to get the commands registered. The T type has to override its equal method.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CommandParser
    public interface Registry<T>
    This interface describes a parser, that has to be able to register and get a command (given a key) and should be able to give a list of all the registered command.
